msgid "Your message is near-identical to others sent previously"
msgstr ""

#: templates/website/problem-similar.html:22
msgid "Please read <a href=\"/about-qa#formletters\">our stance on this issue</a> to understand why sending identikit \"copied and pasted\" messages is detrimental to your campaign."
